text: Ančka Goropenko (29 October 1914 - July 2005) was a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
